Eskom, Vunene Finalizing Terms of Camden Coal Accord, Business Report Says

-- B y   A l a s t a i r   R e e d
-- 
2011-04-06T05:22:48Z

-- http://www.bloomberg.com/news/2011-04-06/eskom-vunene-mining-finalizing-camden-coal-accord-business-report-says.html
Eskom Holdings Ltd. is finalizing
the terms of a five-year coal supply deal for its Camden power
station with Vunene Mining (Pty) Ltd., Business Report said,
citing Hilary Joffe, a spokeswoman for the South African power
utility.  To contact the editor responsible for this story:
